testcaseName: Patient is >18 years and has received the Janssen Covid-19 vaccine
generalDescription: This test case describes when a patient is administered the Janssen Covid-19 vaccine, that the dose is valid. Another dose should be forecast.
reasonForChange: v4.13 - Updated test case to include the forecasting of a Covid-19 booster dose, at an interval of 8 weeks from most recent dose, for individuals who've received only one dose of the Janssen vaccine.
